{
  "stem": "4710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember, because later on, after the selection period, which was those-- the time of the Jewish festivals, coincided with the Jewish festivals.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Not-- not by-- not by just coincidence, the Germans made it especially to-- to hurt the Jews even more.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But afterwards, they stopped the-- stopped the selections in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Stopped the-- the gassing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It came an order from Himmler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in fact, in fact, I was there in the camp when people were already in the gas chambers, and there came the order that they should-- that they-- that the gassing has to stop.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were told, dress again, and-- and-- and leave the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was in the camp when-- when people came back from the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It never happened before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they-- and they had an order that the gassing has to stop.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans are following orders, so they immediately stopped the gassing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took out a group of youngsters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, what-- what I understood at that time, that the Germans, they changed their policies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The reason is because-- because by that time, it must have been October or November, they-- they realized that Auschwitz has to be evacuated very soon because the Russians are near-- getting near.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they have to-- have to avoid-- have to avoid all the-- the signs or the traces of what happened here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, that was only-- only bit of work which I-- which I carried out in my camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was not-- I was never fit to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- but when-- when the gas chambers were-- were destroyed, were-- were demolished, I was working to take away the rubble with carts from the place where the gas chamber [INAUDIBLE] to somewhere else in the open.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
